{"tid":470638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又要多謝蛆国］孔雀牌東莞米粉重金屬鎘超標60% 食安中心籲停用","createTime":"2017-11-16T13:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T15:41:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7df229c2d7e02e573da830b94a66203f998b43","tid":470638,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/210408_7bf2cf04dbb94ec7d5d6ab7c8d73a038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F210408_7bf2cf04dbb94ec7d5d6ab7c8d73a038.jpg&h=f23e1e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國的「孔雀牌」東莞米粉重金屬「鎘」含量超出法例上限60%，呼籲市民立即停止食用受影響批次，業界亦應停用和停售。<br />\n<br />\n受影響的「孔雀牌」東莞米粉由廣宏行有限公司代理進口，經銷商為泰明行有限公司，每包淨含量有400克，批次上印有「此日期前最佳」為2019年6月1日。<br />\n<br />\n食安中心發言人稱是透過恆常食物監察計劃，從深水埗一店鋪抽取該米粉樣本作檢測，結果發現樣本的鎘含量為百萬分之0.16，超出法例上限的法例上限的百萬分之0.1達60%。中心已知會有關商戶並指令將產品停售及下架，進口商正進行回收。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又指，雖然一般食用情況下，進食過該批鎘含量超標的米粉不會對健康造成不良影響，但市民仍應該立即停止食用，中心將會知會業界，並會繼續跟進事件和採取適當行動。市民可於辦公時間致電進口商熱線：9485 5329，查詢產品回收事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171116/57466967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57466967&d=kTs28R88PNCX9IObIZg5NLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=0db09225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57466967&h=031de791\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171116/57466967</a>"},{"pid":"94790ac7002798cc57c82eaee184d44d1c6e8b99","tid":470638,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"Cd超標都話冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118f430